  <mj-body width="800px" background-color="#eee">
    <mj-section background-color="#452966" padding="10px 30px">
      <mj-column width="50%" vertical-align="middle">
        <mj-image align="center" css-class="align-left" width="120px" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/jan2023/logo-header.png" alt="" />
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="50%" vertical-align="middle">
        <mj-text align="center" css-class="align-right" color="#fff" font-size="16px" font-style="italic">
          <p>January 2023 Edition</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section padding="0" background-color="#170521" background-url="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/jan2023/image-banner.png" background-repeat="no-repeat" background-size="contain" background-position="left center" css-class="mbl-hero-banner">
      <mj-column css-class="ml-n60" width="50%" vertical-align="middle">
        <mj-text color="white" padding-left="175px" font-size="20px" line-height="1.25">
          <h1>Locus in Spotlight</h1>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="50%" background-color="#6B3D99" vertical-align="middle" padding="25px" css-class="hero-cont-pad">
        <mj-text color="white" line-height="1.65" css-class="mbl-text-center">
          <p style="margin-top:0px;">With every new year comes a sense of optimism. New opportunities to discover, new markets to explore, and new trends to ride on for delivering growth. From sustainable last-mile fulfillment to the rise of omnichannel retail, stay ahead of the curve with some of the most impactful last-mile trends of 2023.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="align-left mb-13" align="center" href="https://locus.sh/last-mile-delivery-trends/">Read more</mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section padding="0px 30px" background-url="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/jan2023/heading-bg-blue.png" background-repeat="no-repeat" background-size="100% 100%" background-position="center">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text color="white" padding="0px 25px">
          <h2>A Word from our Leaders</h2>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="white">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image width="100px" align="center" css-class="align-left mbl-pt-30" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/profile-img-walter-heil.png" alt="" />
        <mj-image css-class="qm-position" width="50px" align="center" css-class="align-right" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/jan2023/quotation-mark.png" alt="" />
        <mj-text font-size="15px" font-weight="600" font-style="italic" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" css-class="mbl-text-center">
          <p>If you can’t give that power to the driver, it doesn’t do you a lot of good because the driver, the delivery person, is our customer’s touch point to their customer, so we take that very seriously.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="13px" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" css-class="mbl-text-center">
          <p>Your drivers’ well-being is foundational to success at the last-mile. Know how <b>Walter Heil, Senior Vice President - Developed Markets,</b> unpacks this, Locus’ expansion in Mexico, and more.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="align-left mbl-pb-40" padding-bottom="30px" align="center" href="https://www.freightwaves.com/news/locus-sees-major-opportunities-in-mexicos-e-commerce-marketplace">Read more</mj-button>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column css-class="mbl-quote-bg">
        <mj-image width="100px" align="center" css-class="align-left mbl-pt-30" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/profile-pic-01.png" alt="" />
        <mj-image css-class="qm-position" width="50px" align="center" css-class="align-right" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/jan2023/quotation-mark.png" alt="" />
        <mj-text font-size="15px" font-weight="600" font-style="italic" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" css-class="mbl-text-center">
          <p>The competition is fierce, and optimum customer experience has become key to the growth of any retail brand. This is where delivery-linked checkout comes into play.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="13px" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" css-class="mbl-text-center">
          <p>Maximizing post-fulfillment customer delight together with operational efficiency is no more a pipe dream. <b>Nishith Rastogi, Founder and CEO,</b> explains how delivery-linked checkout features can make this a reality for last mile businesses.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="align-left mbl-pb-40" padding-bottom="30px" align="center" href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/blogs/voices/delivery-linked-checkout-a-game-changer-for-retailers-in-india/?source=app&frmapp=yes">Read more</mj-button>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image width="100px" align="center" css-class="align-left mbl-pt-30" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/profile-pic-01.png" alt="" />
        <mj-image css-class="qm-position" width="50px" align="center" css-class="align-right" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/jan2023/quotation-mark.png" alt="" />
        <mj-text font-size="15px" font-weight="600" font-style="italic" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" css-class="mbl-text-center">
          <p>Our recognition in the Gartner Market Guide for Last-Mile Technology Solutions validates our efforts in revolutionizing global last-mile logistics.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="13px" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" css-class="mbl-text-center">
          <p>We are proud to announce that Locus has been listed as a Representative Vendor for the third consecutive year in Gartner® Market Guides. Know all about our end-to-end dispatch management platform that makes</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="align-left mbl-pb-40" padding-bottom="30px" align="center" href="https://blog.locus.sh/locus-identified-in-gartner-for-last-mile-delivery-technology/">Read more</mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

