          <p>New York City is quite a happening city this time of the year! We should know as we would be participating in NRF, the world’s largest retail convention, from Januray 14-17.</p>
          <p>Hear straight from Locus’ leadership team on how retailers can redefine consumer delight at the last mile without compromising on operational efficiency with our API-ready solutions.</p>
