        <mj-text css-class="h-200 mbl-text-center" font-size="15px" font-weight="600" color="white">
          <p class="mw-400">Forward or Backward Scheduling? Make the Right Choice for your Business with our step-by-step guide.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="align-left mbl-pb-40" padding-bottom="30px" align="center" href="https://blog.locus.sh/forward-scheduling-and-backward-scheduling/">Our step-by-step guide</mj-button>
