      <mj-column background-color="#290A38">
        <mj-image css-class="img-fluid" padding="0px" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/jan2023/thought-fuel-resource-2.jpg" alt="" />
        <mj-text css-class="h-200 mbl-text-center" font-size="15px" font-weight="600" color="white">
          <p class="mw-400">Your ability to minimize last-mile delivery exceptions to the largest possible extent will decide the fate of your growth. Here’s our take on delivery exceptions and how to handle them.</p>
