        <mj-button css-class="align-left mbl-pb-40" padding-bottom="30px" align="center" href="https://blog.locus.sh/what-is-delivery-exception/">How to handle</mj-button>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column background-color="#452966">
        <mj-image css-class="img-fluid" padding="0px" src="https://info.locus.sh/hubfs/Emailer%20images/customer-newsletter-template/jan2023/thought-fuel-resource-3.jpg" alt="" />
        <mj-text css-class="h-200 mbl-text-center" font-size="15px" font-weight="600" color="white">
          <p class="mw-400">Know how Retailers can get past challenges to step up their last mile fulfillment game in a highly competitive business environment.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button css-class="align-left mbl-pb-40" padding-bottom="30px" align="center" href="https://blog.locus.sh/how-retailers-in-us-step-up-customer-delivery-experience/">Find out how</mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="white" padding="10px 30px">
